title: Test
summary: This is a multi-line chart with 2 lines representing Common stock, and Preferred stock.
The line for Common stock has the highest values across Year with a mean value of 160.64,
and it peaked at 2013 with a value of 196.9.
Preferred stock mostly had the least y-axis name with a mean value of 160.21,
which peaked at 2013 with a value of 204.15.
Preferred stock reported the highest y-axis name  about 204.15 in Year 2013
Preferred stock reported the lowest y-axis name  about 133.35 in Year 2016
Overall Common stock, and Preferred stock are gradually decreasing,  throughout the Year
The difference of y_axis name between Common stock and Preferred stock is smaller at Year 2018 compared to the Year 2013.
The greatest difference of y_axis name between Common stock and Preferred stock occurs at Year 2015 and the smallest difference occurs at 2018.
